sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor U as User
participant FE as Frontend
participant AIC as AIController
participant AIS as AIService
participant DB as AI Chat Store
participant Router as ProviderRouter
participant LLM as AI Provider

U->>FE: Send question to AI Copilot
FE->>AIC: POST /ai/chat/stream
AIC->>AIS: Handle chat request
AIS->>DB: Save user message and request log
AIS->>Router: Select provider/model
Router-->>AIS: Selected provider
AIS->>LLM: Send prompt and context
loop Stream response chunks
  LLM-->>AIS: Partial response
  AIS-->>FE: SSE chunk/status event
  FE-->>U: Render streaming content
end
AIS->>DB: Save assistant message and AI log
AIS-->>FE: SSE done
FE-->>U: Show final response
